(1486, NULL, 'import', '24268', 'IB Language Ab Initio—German', 'IB Language Ab Initio—German courses prepare students to take the International Baccalaureate exam. These courses focus on developing the linguistic abilities of students with little or no experience with the language of study. Course content includes the study of individuals and society, leisure and work, and urban and rural environments. These courses also provide students with the opportunity to practice and explore this language.', 'No Change', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 1, 1, '2020-05-28 11:22:17', '2020-05-28 11:22:17'),
